{"tid":2085504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文字直播］「岳義士」今早判刑","createTime":"2020-06-30T02:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T03:37:54.000Z","uid":22556,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"98a50888f80f52c5002f139ee711e6c07aa0b986","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"「岳義士」今早判刑 庭外30名親友候籌進庭聽判<br />\n<br />\n去年9月15日北角衝突中，身穿「岳」字上衣、被網民稱為「岳義士」的男子陳以晉，被指持自拍鋁棒襲警並協助其他示威者逃走。他早前承認各一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及襲警罪，並在本月15日被裁定拒捕罪成，遭還柙候判。案件今日在東區裁判法院判刑。"},{"pid":"215b42627afdde4e4a3333bde50e578d26fc45c7","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"👩🏻&zwj;⚖️香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤陳(19)🔥 #判刑（#0915北角 襲警、公眾地方管有攻擊性武器、抗拒警員）<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n控罪2：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n控罪3：抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n<br />\n被指以「自拍棍」襲警並協助 3 名示威者逃走的陳，早前承認頭兩罪，否認抗拒警員罪受審後。6月15日被裁定罪名成立還押，至今日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n公眾已入庭<br />\n等候開庭"},{"pid":"61ae8263bcf4391c37c6f9dd81e93c8110c2fb31","tid":2085504,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"岳義士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823a4a6f3413e802b85b7777fe3c0334ae557b31","tid":2085504,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"7e825dc7089bb5500a6d08a2f709211d918f3f68","tid":2085504,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cbd87de0ebbbf333337da705d3338cef713d360","tid":2085504,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"香淑嫻"},{"pid":"87af3a69216d19a51e6c29b0451f665d95f29fe2","tid":2085504,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964ccf6f17a6d2d60f7a267a408f66e4c4699c1b","tid":2085504,"uid":272898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23a1d7709fe2e1b6fb0cee1eea406eee3d249f59","tid":2085504,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"又係香淑嫻判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba964d9481acfe78da2796b64552e2c2712a090","tid":2085504,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2e7d71fcc42ef6c3b568b2baf637a55a8681fea","tid":2085504,"uid":128179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5f17ed41756b450d671c438018582737e63024","tid":2085504,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd866c1d1e02a602cb044446f12265ab181c7a3","tid":2085504,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e309f99170211015bf3c3e32da455f6cd55bf23","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外西灣河開槍案！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官 <br />\n#轉介文件 <br />\n#1111西灣河 #肇事警員受匿名令保護<br />\n<br />\nD1:周 (21)<br />\nD2:胡 (20)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)D1-2:故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n(2)D1-2:企圖搶劫<br />\n(3)D1:企圖從合法羈押下逃脫<br />\n<br />\n詳細：<br />\n(1)D1-2同被控於19年11月11日在西灣河太安街與筲箕灣道十字路口附近，故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員A <br />\n(2)D1-2同被控於同日同地企圖搶劫A的警槍<br />\n(3)D1被控於同日同地企圖從警員A的合法羈押下逃脫<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">案件押後至7月21日1430時區域法院再訊，期間維持原有條件保釋。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e28ac324846a2e0b810317076118bf91757e6a1b","tid":2085504,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ff63e44b850712eb05d6171d2b89b20b79d58d","tid":2085504,"uid":170438,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦，邊能個會記得？？？"},{"pid":"bbcbbb6f037d4be78348dc04f9048a74f0812506","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:25:21.000Z","msg":"判10個月！"},{"pid":"66ecd7c5e19f2f45e3f30de7da3dc9b103c6f0cd","tid":2085504,"uid":13412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8089366deb5c65a58ef53d9ea4b30a121f62bedc","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"「岳男」陳以晉去年9月在炮台山為拯救其他示威者，用自拍棍襲擊追截的督察，他早前承認襲警及在公眾地方藏有攻擊性武器罪，月中再被裁定拒捕罪成。裁判官香淑嫻今判陳入獄10個月。"},{"pid":"4fb0aa6a61151365e53eb229694605d6818d8915","tid":2085504,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f852834695513972a0215ec0f72d3417f5c321b","tid":2085504,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:26:21.000Z","msg":"佢咁突出十個月係咪唔算重"},{"pid":"a9126caa2b1829c3388ec80c73fbe0c0f3cd2433","tid":2085504,"uid":136988,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"10個月!?? 比我想像中低<br />\n<br />\n仆街大波華唔好覆核呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"2e5026db9cb5defe9dcc672715cdedc4f8fc2315","tid":2085504,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"義士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071beca4cebc203120c4e289eb8e022054841487","tid":2085504,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"岳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88af3ff06dedf2eb624ff7fbbcdd8af054a5d32","tid":2085504,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"情操高尚幾耐話"},{"pid":"5a8454fbb6311a101ad5c730a490048a4a6a493b","tid":2085504,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"岳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實扣埋還押/行為良好係咪可以年底放"},{"pid":"43622a8e8c1d13b8fef14d77f3bdda811ef7989e","tid":2085504,"uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"判10個月  詳情如下 <br />\n<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n👤陳(19)🔥 #判刑（#0915北角 襲警、公眾地方管有攻擊性武器、抗拒警員）<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n控罪2：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n控罪3：抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景報告，勞教中心報告，被告無異議<br />\n<br />\n背景報告：<br />\n今年19屋企人同住，讀書一般，學校活躍份子，熱心課外活動。<br />\n後悔反省，他並非參加遊行示威。當晚出街見到警員將人推入巷裡，一時衝動做出一二控罪。明白犯錯今後循規蹈矩，不做社會不接受的事情。父母經過長時間擔心，希望儘量輕判。<br />\n<br />\n勞教中心報告：<br />\n確認醫療情況，醫生認為被告不適合勞教中心。被告明白不適合勞教中心，監禁難免。判刑考慮明白事件嚴重性，家庭因素。<br />\n<br />\n求請：<br />\n希望考慮三項控罪一時衝動，並非有預謀。被告年齡，面對即時監禁不容易，考慮到年紀尚小，屋企管教一向足夠。希望三方面考慮 ，無刑事定罪紀錄，年紀輕，案件並非不嚴重但也非同類最重，探員傷勢也非十分嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n官判詞：<br />\n顯示背景良好，過往沒有任何刑事定罪紀錄，參考相關判刑案例，綜合以上，判處：<br />\n<br />\n第一項控罪，量刑起點12個月監禁，認罪扣減1/3，為8個月<br />\n第二項控罪8個月，當庭認罪 1/4扣減，為6個月<br />\n同時發生一二同期執行，兩項控罪共判8個月。<br />\n第三項控罪 判9個月監禁，無扣減，其中兩個月與第一二項控罪分期執行。<br />\n即🔴三罪總共刑期10個月🔴"},{"pid":"105476b7f9f8d059a8da3718bf29818405401cb3","tid":2085504,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4327c9e9f22234c546f3fd76bf7ab81c90432671","tid":2085504,"uid":187197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"岳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10個月真係比我想像中低<br />\n社工都1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb695b8c88cd5ddc11153c2266c30208b2bfbc79","tid":2085504,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728ab9fd903851e6f4042e85bbddf76c050ffbaa","tid":2085504,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:29:51.000Z","msg":"壁屋見"},{"pid":"f6029d96869f3bbb9ab348973064188e54f62d0a","tid":2085504,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07efb7f55c8b5fa8f86de5947a17c4f8d6997275","tid":2085504,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":3,"scor